Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:10.70,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,真白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.33,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:13.73,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:45.96,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:47.26,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:48.70,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:49.63,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:19.99,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:22.80,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,妳撐得漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:24.70,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,那是愛瑞斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:25.83,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,珠洲的黃玉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:28.80,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,前途相當「五量」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:30.88,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙 是「無量」啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:33.40,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 那邊的珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.70,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.44,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,就是力量和技巧還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.58,ZW,NTP,0,0,0,,毅力～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:08.47,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:12.54,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:24.05,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:30.26,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}滿盈內心開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:37.90,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:41.54,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:45.58,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:54.03,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:59.39,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:07.26,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:12.87,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}只要能踏出小小的一步你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.74,OP ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}就是嶄新的我
